title: Watch "Taylor Swift" Scare the Bejesus Out of Selena Gomez
text:
​This week, Ellen DeGeneres had Selena Gomez on her show, where the two talked boys, her lupus diagnosis, body-shaming, and how to join Taylor Swift's squad. But, because this is Ellen, talk show host plus expert prankster, Selena didn't have just a normal interview. Ellen scared her twice … and really, really got her.
